==Finnish==
===Pronunciation===
IPA: /ˈjɑlkɑ/
===Etymology===
From the same Finno-Ugric root ''[[*jalka]]'' as Estonian ''[[jalg]]'', Northern Sami [[juolgi]] and Hungarian ''[[gyalog]]''
===Noun===
'''jalka'''

# [[foot]]
# [[leg]]
# [[base]], [[pedestal]]

